      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA OLD MATE (2) continues to race in super honest form hitting the frame at eight of 21 career runs, winning two back before finishing second last time (29.70) over 515m at this track. Performs well off this draw. Has the ability and expected to prove tough to beat again. RITZA KRIS (1) goes very well here starting five times for three wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (22.50) when third at Gosford in a Grade 5. Looks a key chance on best figures. QUICK THINKIN' (8) was well backed last start but ran below expectations when sixth (25.69), beaten 11 lengths. The form out of his last race has been franked. Worth another chance. DAISY'S CHARM (3) placed last time out so worth considering.",
